snippet.title: Riftbound - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Riftbound, the action packed lane defense game, OUT NOW on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1588340/Riftbound/?utm_source=yt_launch

Defend against waves of undead by choosing the right mix of defenders, spells and upgrades from five schools of magic.  Explosive, action packed battles and deep strategy.

#Riftbound
